'accès à l\'ensemble des papiers administratifs et comptables,</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">l\'obtention du droit de vote, </span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">la possibilité de se faire élire pour s\'engager davantage dans l\'association,</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">l\'engagement personnel lors des démarches communes (distributions de flyer, autocollant, collecte de matériel)\r\n</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Pour ce faire, une cotisation annuelle fixe de 20 euros est obligatoire.\r\n</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"133\" title=\"CONTACT BENEVOLE\"]','ESPACE BENEVOLE / MEMBRE','','inherit','closed','closed','','51-revision-v1','','','2016-03-18 11:07:14','2016-03-18 10:07:14','',51,'http://localhost:8888/b2com/51-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(248,1,'2016-03-18 11:09:53','2016-03-18 10:09:53','<h2><span style=\"color: #33a949;\">INFORMATIONS SUR LES DONATIONS</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"4\" title=\"CONTACT ENTREPRISE\"]','ESPACE ENTREPRISE','','inherit','closed','closed','','54-revision-v1','','','2016-03-18 11:09:53','2016-03-18 10:09:53','',54,'http://localhost:8888/b2com/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(249,1,'2016-03-18 11:19:54','2016-03-18 10:19:54','<h2><span style=\"color: #33a949;\">TOUS SUR LES DONS</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"4\" title=\"CONTACT ENTREPRISE\"]','ESPACE ENTREPRISE','','inherit','closed','closed','','54-revision-v1','','','2016-03-18 11:19:54','2016-03-18 10:19:54','',54,'http://localhost:8888/b2com/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(250,1,'2016-03-18 11:20:04','2016-03-18 10:20:04','<h2><span style=\"color: #33a949;\">TOUS SAVOIR S